{"tid":686667,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東鐵大媽舌戰拖行李青年 「唔好話香港人成日蝦你哋」","createTime":"2018-06-01T13:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T13:32:06.000Z","uid":2547,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"af95377fd0489be10af704ec882692af55e5de5d","tid":686667,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:27:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9ZlgYhYBfH0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9ZlgYhYBfH0&d=KZr3dx1hxODI1fEvkQuDHcmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=e21b6e5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9ZlgYhYBfH0</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/01/212652_6fe975248405bed6ab1a54aafdade4a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F01%2F212652_6fe975248405bed6ab1a54aafdade4a2.png&h=e020d244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上流傳一段片段，一名本地婦人在東鐵一列頭等車廂内，因對面一名青年攜帶行李車佔用了空間，而婦人的腳踢撞到行李車，引起雙方當場對罵。婦人氣勢淩厲，連珠炮發「唔好話香港人成日蝦你哋」，而對方亦反擊「女人畀你影衰」。結果雙方僵持不下，一班網民都勸「打和喇」。<br />\n<br />\nfacebook流傳片段，雖然無從得知爭執的起源，片段中見到一名中年婦人與對面一名年輕男子對罵，年輕男子無奈指「請你挪開個袋啫，咁小事都咁大聲，個袋砸到我對腳咋嘛」，然後婦人就怒斥「我梗係要咁大聲，唔大聲你又唔聽」。婦人又反擊「你隻腳唔伸埋嚟點會砸到你啊」，「你有行李Ok，你應該自己去處理，點解要佔人哋個位」。<br />\n<br />\n之後越演越烈，婦人更有人身攻擊之意味， 「我仲以為你唔識講廣東話」、「唔好話香港人成日蝦你哋喇，你哋要用下個腦，諗下條件規矩」。於是男子反駁，「講完未啊，我香港人嚟架」，於是婦人立即還擊「我唔理你咩人啊」。<br />\n<br />\n網民見到公說公有理，婆說婆有理，都覺得無從入手，笑言「坐頭等，不過就唔見有頭等既質素囉」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a4a55083a59c82a84bd2de2db331fec8a8c6bc","tid":686667,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:28:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bca52f2efebc9169a179386696172a5943cbb77","tid":686667,"uid":1938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29a4a55083a59c82a84bd2de2db331fec8a8c6bc","tid":686667,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:28:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:32:06.000Z","msg":"呀又真係駁你唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}